<topic id="communicating_with_reviewers">
    <title>Communicating with Reviewers</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Content Author Guide<indexterm>Communicating with
          Reviewers</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Communicating with Reviewers</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
    <body>
    <p>As the <b>Content Author</b>, to communicate with <b>Reviewers</b> directly in the <ph
        keyref="product"/> interface, follow these steps:<ol>
        <li>In the <uicontrol>Content Fusion Tasks Manager</uicontrol> view, click on the name of
          the particular task. This opens the task details in the <ph keyref="product"/> interface
          in your default browser.</li>
        <li>Click the <uicontrol>Add Message</uicontrol> button and enter a message you want all
            <b>Reviewers</b> to see.</li>
        <li>When finished entering your message, click <uicontrol>Add</uicontrol>.</li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
</topic>
